    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《King’s Bounty: Warriors of the North》是《King’s Bounty》系列的一部独立作品，同时也是《King’s Bounty: The Legend》世界观下的剧情续作。距离原作冒险已经过去了一代人，但恩多里亚的和平依然脆弱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新的威胁从冰封的北方崛起。亡灵大军在区域内蔓延，步步逼近王国的核心。玩家将扮演奥拉夫，一名维京战士、狂怒者托蒙德最年轻的儿子，肩负着保卫家园、阻止亡灵推进的使命。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/203350/extras/169abcd3bb294851219d93d82fc366c5.poster.avif?t=1770723544\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/203350/extras/169abcd3bb294851219d93d82fc366c5.webm?t=1770723544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/203350/extras/169abcd3bb294851219d93d82fc366c5.mp4?t=1770723544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最初的地方冲突很快演变为席卷恩多里亚北境的大规模战役。你必须解放诺尔迪格之地，在冰封岛屿、古老要塞与战火肆虐的区域之间穿行，并为愈发危险的战斗精心准备你的军队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索在一个庞大的手工打造世界中以实时方式进行，而战斗则以深度回合制战术形式展开。随着敌人愈加强大、失误愈发难以挽回，站位、士气、单位协同与战前准备变得至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Warriors of the North》通过符文魔法扩展了系列的战术核心。这一全新系统允许单位在战斗中消耗符文以获得强大的临时增益。若在合适的时机使用，这些效果能够扭转战局，为战略决策增添新的层次。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/203350/extras/f1144ca1af3f35dcf5a1955dbe7877e6.poster.avif?t=1770723544\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/203350/extras/f1144ca1af3f35dcf5a1955dbe7877e6.webm?t=1770723544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/203350/extras/f1144ca1af3f35dcf5a1955dbe7877e6.mp4?t=1770723544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奥拉夫并非孤身奋战。他有五位女武神相助，这些强力同伴提供独特的加成与能力。如何利用她们的优势，将成为战场与长期成长规划中的重要战略选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >北方主题引入了狂战士、吟游诗人等全新维京风格单位，强化的狂怒机制，以及一条围绕持续升级展开的战役。凭借更阴暗的基调、扩展的系统和鲜明的个性，《King’s Bounty: Warriors of the North》在继承《The Legend》精神的同时，带来了更深度、更具挑战性的战术体验与全新的战略视角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/203350/extras/bac04e8ba6f3a49f98b3b2419ff4e9ba.poster.avif?t=1770723544\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/203350/extras/bac04e8ba6f3a49f98b3b2419ff4e9ba.webm?t=1770723544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/203350/extras/bac04e8ba6f3a49f98b3b2419ff4e9ba.mp4?t=1770723544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>独立的维京战役。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在恩多里亚的世界中体验全新篇章，聚焦冰封的北方土地与亡灵入侵。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扮演维京英雄奥拉夫。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >率领“狂怒者”托蒙德最年轻的儿子，将诺尔迪格从亡灵势力手中解放出来。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>符文魔法系统。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新的战术层面，允许单位在战斗中消耗符文以获得强大的临时加成。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>五位女武神同伴。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提供独特加成与能力的战略型同伴，影响战斗表现与长期规划。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全新维京风格单位与强化的狂怒机制。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指挥狂战士、吟游诗人等北方单位，专为激进、节奏驱动的战斗而设计。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>庞大的手工打造北方世界。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索冰封群岛、古老要塞与战火肆虐的地区，充满任务、秘密与高难度遭遇。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深度回合制战术战斗。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗更看重站位、单位协同、符文的合理运用以及周密准备，而非单纯的蛮力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
